About Us

Story about our hospital

About our hospital

Established in 1995, Lakshmi Hospital in Bengaluru has grown from a modest clinic into a leading healthcare institution, delivering exceptional medical services with compassion. Committed to accessible and top-tier care, we continuously enhance our services, facilities, and technology to meet evolving patient needs. Trusted for over two decades, Lakshmi Hospital embodies excellence in healthcare, fostering countless success stories and providing hope to families in need. Upholding integrity, compassion, and innovation, we aim to set new standards in healthcare delivery, making a significant impact on our community's well-being.

Frequently Asked Questions

What are your visiting hours ?

Our visiting hours for in-patient wards are from 10:00 AM to 12:00 PM and 5:00 PM to 7:00 PM.

How can I schedule an appointment ?

To schedule an appointment, you can call our hospital at 080-2333 3241 or visit our website to book online.

Do you accept health insurance plans ?

Yes, Lakshmi Hospital accepts various health insurance plans. Please inquire at the reception desk for details.

What medical specialties do you offer consultations in ?

We offer consultations in a range of medical specialties including General Medicine, Obstetrics and Gynecology, Pediatrics, General Surgery, Orthopedics, and more.

Are your facilities accessible for patients with disabilities ?

Yes, Lakshmi Hospital is equipped with facilities to accommodate patients with disabilities. Please inform our staff in advance so we can assist you accordingly.
